end_user_data_statement:
Application Channel: The ID of the text channel where applications are submitted. This is stored using application_channel setting. 
 Questions: A dictionary that maps role IDs to a list of questions associated with that role. This is stored using the questions setting.
Applications: A dictionary that maps role IDs to another dictionary, which maps member IDs to their application responses. This is stored using the applications setting.
